Text:
Hi Mary Jane! 

This is Steve, Melissa Bemer’s husband. 

I just landed in Charleston, SC. I’m playing the Cougar Point at Kiawah Island tomorrow late-morning and I already have a tee time. 

I just remembered that you were able to get me a discount a couple years ago when I played the Ocean Course. I was curious if you had the same ability to apply a discount to the round tomorrow??

Totally no problem if not! Thought I’d ask just in case.  And I hope all is well with you 😀
Sorry Steve , but unable to get this point .Renters still in for Easter & considered high season due to holiday. Have a great round ⛳️
